We now move on to discuss the lower six detectors (E–J) of LND which are mounted in two different sandwich configurations. In one, detectors E & F and G & H clamp a very thin (≈20μm\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
